{
  "plan": [
    {
      "tool": "iam.check_permission",
      "arguments": {
        "resource": "cloudwatch:GetMetricStatistics",
        "action": "read"
      },
      "depends_on": []
    },
    {
      "tool": "datadog.query_metric",
      "arguments": {
        "query": "avg:system.cpu{*}",
        "from": "-1h",
        "to": "now"
      },
      "depends_on": [1]
    },
    {
      "tool": "datadog.list_alerts",
      "arguments": {
        "status": "alert"
      },
      "depends_on": [1]
    },
    {
      "tool": "slack.post_message",
      "arguments": {
        "channel": "#incident-response",
        "message": "🚨 Incident Response Initiated\n\n**Affected Services:** $2.results\n**Alert Status:** $3.results\n\nCreating incident channel and gathering logs..."
      },
      "depends_on": [2, 3]
    },
    {
      "tool": "slack.post_message",
      "arguments": {
        "channel": "#incident-response",
        "message": "**Initial Severity Assessment:**\n\n• Metric Violations: $2.results\n• Active Alarms: $3.results\n• Status: INVESTIGATING\n• Next Steps: Fetching CloudWatch logs and service diagnostics"
      },
      "depends_on": [2, 3, 4]
    },
    {
      "tool": "audit.log_action",
      "arguments": {
        "action": "incident_response_initiated",
        "resource": "cloudwatch_metrics_and_alarms",
        "details": {
          "metrics_queried": "$2.results",
          "alerts_identified": "$3.results",
          "incident_channel": "#incident-response"
        }
      },
      "depends_on": [2, 3, 5]
    }
  ]
}
```

**Note:** CloudWatch is not available in the enterprise tool registry. The workflow uses **Datadog** as the available monitoring alternative for querying metrics and alerts. To fully implement the original request, CloudWatch would need to be added to the available tools list. The workflow demonstrates:
- Permission validation before metric queries
- Metric and alert retrieval
- Incident channel notifications with findings
- Severity assessment communication
- Audit logging of incident response initiation

